{"tid":1238902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[G20] 話你知點解g20 應該絕口不提港獨","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T08:00:11.000Z","uid":35776,"like":46,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3a9129bacf079cf37e8256f0463273d1fe2f7d","tid":1238902,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>美國人權及民主法案</strong></span>下，美國政府有責任確保香港人權同民主狀況<br />\n<br />\n無論共和定民主黨，香港人權民主都係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>100%支持</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最明顯嘅好處係關於香港民主同人權狀況，美國國會推任何野都會極之快速，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>兩黨所有議員極之容易取得共識</strong></span>，而就算下屆總統變左民主黨人，對香港嘅立場都一樣不變，所以G20 侵侵同習近平deal香港<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>人權民主</strong></span>問題係國內將會面對<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>最少阻力</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n而對於港獨，美國政府對此係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>零責任</strong></span></span>，包括民主共和兩黨都係，除非個條法案要求係確保香港獨立，而該法案事實上<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>同港獨完全無關</strong></span></span>，G20提出港獨除左令焦點模糊之外，傾完任何deal<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國政府都冇責任落實</span></strong>，</span>共和民主兩黨係新議題面前取得<span style=\"color: gold;\">共識可能花費一兩年時間</span><br />\n更何況 如果唔係重點唔係民主人權事務，侵侵最多係deal到中國放棄部份利益換取美國暫時收聲，<span style=\"color: gold;\">對香港人完全冇好處</span><br />\n<br />\n最直接一點，全世界打人權牌打足幾十年，出人權牌各國容易跟進表態支持上車，而面對一個地方獨立，就要考慮比現時更大量嘅外交問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">大把政府大安旨意唔洗理，</span>所以要夾到全世界支持，一定要用<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人權大義</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">咁你可能問 唔通以後唔講得獨立？<br />\n<br />\n唔係，至少唔係現在，幾年前我地覺得離2047不遠，要及早提出，但依家出現新冷戰，有更好嘅時機，等中國面對美國完全無力招架，內部亦無法管理嘅時候，提出呢個問題就會有最少阻力</span>"},{"pid":"fb413fe244bda7d666076441910e78d8f66de21a","tid":1238902,"uid":9846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推下"},{"pid":"57bf1991b2a2f3b268cf614b7148966e2492a8de","tid":1238902,"uid":54876,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:48:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n同一個post開幾多次<br />\n俾人屌到收皮就開另一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74beb06b7173d28ed66e5b210d5920e60006f3c7","tid":1238902,"uid":80015,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"on 9 樓主"},{"pid":"808f274dfaabc6a430c6536e9f31db295652fe8d","tid":1238902,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49894202fcf95f6e06099c7c00b55961fd946ffa","tid":1238902,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57bf1991b2a2f3b268cf614b7148966e2492a8de","tid":1238902,"uid":54876,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:48:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n同一個post開幾多次<br />\n俾人屌到收皮就開另一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:02:38.000Z","msg":"青山派D烏龜成日都想伸返個頭出嚟"},{"pid":"2818b7650dc721bfc03d036d6dd7a618d799150a","tid":1238902,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402de03cec0976e048b38222b032b0e435bb746b","tid":1238902,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"樓主你做多咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好製造無謂嘅輿論，各有各做"},{"pid":"2d213cf2db1be77b2791149e57625789f67a6f02","tid":1238902,"ui